@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

title OpenData Processing Sequence

actor User
participant CLI
participant Application
participant Pipeline
participant DatasetPlugin
participant Repository

User -> CLI: Execute command
CLI -> Application: Run dataset
Application -> Pipeline: Execute
Pipeline -> DatasetPlugin: Extract / validate / transform
Pipeline -> Repository: Load records
Repository --> Pipeline: Import result
Pipeline --> Application: Pipeline result
Application --> CLI: Exit status

@enduml
